name: MoodTrack
0:
”Alexa, tell Mood Track that I feel great”
”Alexa, ask Mood Track how have I been feeling this week”
”Alexa, ask Mood Track how are other people feeling”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: mood track
des: Mood Track tracks your moods and feelings so that it can provide statistics on your mood and energy levels in specific periods, both recent and historical. It also provides snapshots of aggregate moods of other users throughout the world.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
